quran[227]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,(tsm) sabaq alkalam ealaa alhrwf almqtet fi 'awal surat albqrt
  26,2,hdhh ayat alquran almwddih likuli shay' alfasil bayn alhudaa waldlal
  26,3,"lelk - 'ayuha alrasul - min shdt hrsk ealaa hdaythm muhlik nfsk; li'anahum lm ysddiqu bik walam yaemaluu bhdyk, fala tafeal dhlk"
  26,4,"'in nasha nunazil ealaa almukadhibin min qawmak min alsama' mejzt mkhwwift lahum tljyhm 'iilaa al'iyman, ftsyr 'aenaqihim khadet dhlylt, wlknna lm nasha dhlk; fa'iina al'iiman alnafe hu al'iiman bialghayb akhtyarana"
  26,5,"wma yaji' hwla' almushrikin almukadhibin min dhikr min alrhmn muhdath 'inzalh, shyyana baed shy', yamuruhum wynhahm, wydhkrhm bialdiyn alhaqi 'iilaa 'aeraduu enh, walam yqblwh"
  26,6,"fqd kdhdhabu bialquran wasthzwu bh, fasayatihim 'akhbar al'amr aldhy kanuu yastahziuwn bih wayaskharun mnh, wsyhll bihim aleadhab jaza'an tmrdhm ealaa rbhm"
  26,7,"akdhbu walam yanzuruu 'iilaa al'ard alati 'anbatna fiha min kuli nawe hasan nafe min alnbat, la yuqadar ealaa 'inbath 'iilaa raba alealmyn? 'iina fi 'iikhraj alnbat min al'ard ladlalt wadihatan ealaa kamal qudrat allh, wama kan 'akthar alqawm mwmnyn. wa'iina rabak lahu aleaziz ealaa kl mkhlwq, alrahim aldhy wasieat rahmatih kl shy'"
  26,8,"akdhbu walam yanzuruu 'iilaa al'ard alati 'anbatna fiha min kuli nawe hasan nafe min alnbat, la yuqadar ealaa 'inbath 'iilaa raba alealmyn? 'iina fi 'iikhraj alnbat min al'ard ladlalt wadihatan ealaa kamal qudrat allh, wama kan 'akthar alqawm mwmnyn. wa'iina rabak lahu aleaziz ealaa kl mkhlwq, alrahim aldhy wasieat rahmatih kl shy'"
  26,9,"akdhbu walam yanzuruu 'iilaa al'ard alati 'anbatna fiha min kuli nawe hasan nafe min alnbat, la yuqadar ealaa 'inbath 'iilaa raba alealmyn? 'iina fi 'iikhraj alnbat min al'ard ladlalt wadihatan ealaa kamal qudrat allh, wama kan 'akthar alqawm mwmnyn. wa'iina rabak lahu aleaziz ealaa kl mkhlwq, alrahim aldhy wasieat rahmatih kl shy'"
  26,10,"wadhkr - 'ayuha alrasul - lqwmk 'iidh nada rabik mwsa: 'an ayt alqawm alzalmyn, qawm frewn, waqul lhm: 'alaa yakhafun eiqab allah teala, wytrkwn maa hum ealayh min alkufr waldlal?"
  26,11,"wadhkr - 'ayuha alrasul - lqwmk 'iidh nada rabik mwsa: 'an ayt alqawm alzalmyn, qawm frewn, waqul lhm: 'alaa yakhafun eiqab allah teala, wytrkwn maa hum ealayh min alkufr waldlal?"
  26,12,"qal mwsa: rabi 'iiniy 'akhaf 'an ykdhbwny fi alrsalt, wymla sadri alghmm ltkdhybhm 'iyay, wala yantaliq lisani baldewt farsil jbryl bialwahy 'iilaa 'akhi harwn; lyeawnny. walahum ealaya dhanb fi qutil rajul mnhm, wahu alqbty, fa'akhaf 'an yqtlwny bh"
  26,13,"qal mwsa: rabi 'iiniy 'akhaf 'an ykdhbwny fi alrsalt, wymla sadri alghmm ltkdhybhm 'iyay, wala yantaliq lisani baldewt farsil jbryl bialwahy 'iilaa 'akhi harwn; lyeawnny. walahum ealaya dhanb fi qutil rajul mnhm, wahu alqbty, fa'akhaf 'an yqtlwny bh"
  26,14,"qal mwsa: rabi 'iiniy 'akhaf 'an ykdhbwny fi alrsalt, wymla sadri alghmm ltkdhybhm 'iyay, wala yantaliq lisani baldewt farsil jbryl bialwahy 'iilaa 'akhi harwn; lyeawnny. walahum ealaya dhanb fi qutil rajul mnhm, wahu alqbty, fa'akhaf 'an yqtlwny bh"
  26,15,"qal allah lmwsa: kla ln yqtlwk, waqad ajbt tlbk fi harwn, fadhhaba balmejzat aldalt ealaa sdqkma, 'iinaa maeakum balelm walhfz walnsrt mstmewn. fatia fireawn faqula lh: 'iinaa mrsalan 'iilayk wa'iilaa qawmak min rabi alealmyn: 'ana 'atruk bani 'israyyl; lydhhbu mena"
  26,16,"qal allah lmwsa: kla ln yqtlwk, waqad ajbt tlbk fi harwn, fadhhaba balmejzat aldalt ealaa sdqkma, 'iinaa maeakum balelm walhfz walnsrt mstmewn. fatia fireawn faqula lh: 'iinaa mrsalan 'iilayk wa'iilaa qawmak min rabi alealmyn: 'ana 'atruk bani 'israyyl; lydhhbu mena"
  26,17,"qal allah lmwsa: kla ln yqtlwk, waqad ajbt tlbk fi harwn, fadhhaba balmejzat aldalt ealaa sdqkma, 'iinaa maeakum balelm walhfz walnsrt mstmewn. fatia fireawn faqula lh: 'iinaa mrsalan 'iilayk wa'iilaa qawmak min rabi alealmyn: 'ana 'atruk bani 'israyyl; lydhhbu mena"
  26,18,"qal fireawn lmwsa mmtnana elyh: 'alam nurabbik fi mnazlna sghyrana, wmktht fi reaytna sinin min eumurk wartkbt jnaytan bqtlk rajulaan min qawmi hin drbth wdfeth, wa'ant min aljahdyn niemati almnkryn rbwbyty?"
  26,19,"qal fireawn lmwsa mmtnana elyh: 'alam nurabbik fi mnazlna sghyrana, wmktht fi reaytna sinin min eumurk wartkbt jnaytan bqtlk rajulaan min qawmi hin drbth wdfeth, wa'ant min aljahdyn niemati almnkryn rbwbyty?"
  26,20,"qal musaa mjybana lfrewn: felt ma dhkrt qabl 'an yuhi allah 'ily, wybethny rasulana fkhrjt min baynakum farrana 'iilaa \"mdyn\", lmma khafat 'ana tqtlwny bima felt min ghyr eamd, fawahab li rabiy tfdla minh alnubuat walelm, wajaealani min almrslyn. watilk altarbiat fi baytik taeudduha niemat mink elya, waqad jaealat bani 'iisrayiyl ebydana tdhbh 'abna'ahum wtsthyy nsa'hm?"
  26,21,"qal musaa mjybana lfrewn: felt ma dhkrt qabl 'an yuhi allah 'ily, wybethny rasulana fkhrjt min baynakum farrana 'iilaa \"mdyn\", lmma khafat 'ana tqtlwny bima felt min ghyr eamd, fawahab li rabiy tfdla minh alnubuat walelm, wajaealani min almrslyn. watilk altarbiat fi baytik taeudduha niemat mink elya, waqad jaealat bani 'iisrayiyl ebydana tdhbh 'abna'ahum wtsthyy nsa'hm?"
  26,22,"qal musaa mjybana lfrewn: felt ma dhkrt qabl 'an yuhi allah 'ily, wybethny rasulana fkhrjt min baynakum farrana 'iilaa \"mdyn\", lmma khafat 'ana tqtlwny bima felt min ghyr eamd, fawahab li rabiy tfdla minh alnubuat walelm, wajaealani min almrslyn. watilk altarbiat fi baytik taeudduha niemat mink elya, waqad jaealat bani 'iisrayiyl ebydana tdhbh 'abna'ahum wtsthyy nsa'hm?"
  26,23,"qal fireawn lmwsa: wama rabu alealamin aldhy tddaey 'anak rswlh?"
  26,24,"qal mwsa: hu malik wmdbr alsmwat wal'ard wama bynhma, 'iin kuntum muwqinin bdhlk, faminu"
  26,25,"qal fireawn liman hawlah min ashraf qwmh: 'alaa tasmaeun mqalt musaa alejybt biwujud rabi sway?"
  26,26,"qal mwsa: alrb aldhy 'adeukum 'iilayh hu aladhi khalaqakum wakhalaq aba'akum alawlyn, fkyf taebudun man hu mkhlwq mthlkm, walah aba' qad fnu kabaykm?"
  26,27,"qal fireawn lkhasth ystthyr ghdbhm; ltkdhyb musaa 'iyah: 'iina rasulakum aladhi 'ursil 'iilaykum lmjnwn, yatakalam klamana la yueqal"
  26,28,"qal mwsa: rabu almashriq walmaghrib wama baynahuma wama yakun fihima min nuwr wzlmt, whdha ystwjb al'iiman bih wahdah 'iin kuntum min 'ahl aleaql waltdbr"
  26,29,"qal fireawn lmwsa mhddana lh: layin atakhadht 'ilhana ghayri lasjnnk mae man sjnt"
  26,30,"qal mwsa: atjelny min almsjwnyn, walaw jituk bbrhan qatie yatabayan minh sdqy?"
  26,31,"qal frewn: fat bih 'iin kunt min alsaadiqin fi dewak"
  26,32,"falqa musaa easah fthwlt thebanana hqyqyana, lays tmwyhana kama yafeal alshrt, wa'akhraj yadah min jybh fa'iidha hi bayda' kalthlj min ghyr brs, tabhar alnazryn"
  26,33,"falqa musaa easah fthwlt thebanana hqyqyana, lays tmwyhana kama yafeal alshrt, wa'akhraj yadah min jybh fa'iidha hi bayda' kalthlj min ghyr brs, tabhar alnazryn"
  26,34,"qal fireawn lashraf qawmih khashyat 'ana ywmnu: 'iina musaa lasahr mahr, yurid 'an yukhrijakum bisihrih min ardkm, fa'aya shay' tshyrwn bih fi shanuh 'atabie raykm fyh?"
  26,35,"qal fireawn lashraf qawmih khashyat 'ana ywmnu: 'iina musaa lasahr mahr, yurid 'an yukhrijakum bisihrih min ardkm, fa'aya shay' tshyrwn bih fi shanuh 'atabie raykm fyh?"
  26,36,"qal lah qwmh: akhkhir 'amr musaa wharwn, warsil fi almadayin jndana jameyn llshrt, yatuk bkll man ajad alshr, wtfwwaq fi merfth"
  26,37,"qal lah qwmh: akhkhir 'amr musaa wharwn, warsil fi almadayin jndana jameyn llshrt, yatuk bkll man ajad alshr, wtfwwaq fi merfth"
  26,38,"fajume alshrt, whuddid lahum waqt melwm, hu waqt aldha min yawm alziynat aldhy ytfrghwn fih min ashghalhm, wyjtmewn wytzyanwn; wdhlk lilaijtimae bmwsa. whuthth alnaas ealaa alajtmae; 'amalaan fi 'an takun alghalbat llshrt"
  26,39,"fajume alshrt, whuddid lahum waqt melwm, hu waqt aldha min yawm alziynat aldhy ytfrghwn fih min ashghalhm, wyjtmewn wytzyanwn; wdhlk lilaijtimae bmwsa. whuthth alnaas ealaa alajtmae; 'amalaan fi 'an takun alghalbat llshrt"
  26,40,"'iinana natmae 'an takun alghalbat llshrt, fnthbt ealaa dynna"
  26,41,"flma ja' alsaharat fireawn qaluu lh: a'in lana lajrana min maal 'aw jah, 'in kunaa nahn alghalibin lmwsa?"
  26,42,"qal frewn: nem lakum eindi ma tlbtm min ajr, wa'iinakum hinayidh lamin almuqarabin ldya"
  26,43,"qal musaa llshrt mrydana 'ibtal sihrihim w'izhar 'ana ma ja' bih lays shrana: 'alquu ma turidun 'ilqa'h min alshr"
  26,44,"falqau hibaluhum wesyahm, wkhuyil lilnaas 'anaha hyaat tsea, wa'aqsamuu bieizat fireawn qaylyn: 'iinana lanahn alghalbwn"
  26,45,"falqa musaa esah, fa'iidha hi hayat ezymt, tbtle ma sdr minhum min 'iifk wtzwyr"
  26,46,"flma shahaduu dhlk, welmu 'anah lays min tmwyh alshrt, aminuu biallah wsjdu lh, wqalu: amnna birabi alealamin rabi musaa wharwn"
  26,47,"flma shahaduu dhlk, welmu 'anah lays min tmwyh alshrt, aminuu biallah wsjdu lh, wqalu: amnna birabi alealamin rabi musaa wharwn"
  26,48,"flma shahaduu dhlk, welmu 'anah lays min tmwyh alshrt, aminuu biallah wsjdu lh, wqalu: amnna birabi alealamin rabi musaa wharwn"
  26,49,"qal fireawn llshrt mstnkrana: amantum lmwsa bighayr 'iidhan mny, waqal mwhmana ann fiel musaa shr: 'iinah lakabirukum aladhi ellamkm alshr, falasawf taelamun ma yunazil bikum mn eqab: laqtenn 'aydiakum wa'arjulakum min khlaf: biqate alyad alyumnaa walrjl alyusraa 'aw eaks dhlk, wlaslbnnakm ajmeyn"
  26,50,"qal alsaharat lfrewn: la darar ealayna fima ylhqna min eiqab aldnya, 'iinaa rajieun 'iilaa rabana fyetyna alnaeim almqym. 'iinaa narju 'an yaghfir lana rabuna khatayana min alshirk wghyrh; lkwnna 'awal almuminin fi qwmk"
  26,51,"qal alsaharat lfrewn: la darar ealayna fima ylhqna min eiqab aldnya, 'iinaa rajieun 'iilaa rabana fyetyna alnaeim almqym. 'iinaa narju 'an yaghfir lana rabuna khatayana min alshirk wghyrh; lkwnna 'awal almuminin fi qwmk"
  26,52,"wawha allah 'iilaa musaa ealayh alslam: 'an sir laylana biman aman min bani 'israyyl; li'ana fireawn wajunuduh mtbewkm hataa la ydrkwkm qabl wswlkm 'iilaa albhr"
  26,53,farsl fireawn jndh- hin blghh masir bani 'israyyl- yajmaeun jyshh min madayin mmlkth
  26,54,"qal frewn: 'iina bani 'iisrayiyl aladhin frru mae musaa latayft hqyrt qalilat aledd, wa'iinahum lmalywn sdwrna ghyzana; hayth khalfu dynna, wkhrju bighayr 'idhnna, wa'iinaa lajamie mtyqzwn mstedwn lhm"
  26,55,"qal frewn: 'iina bani 'iisrayiyl aladhin frru mae musaa latayft hqyrt qalilat aledd, wa'iinahum lmalywn sdwrna ghyzana; hayth khalfu dynna, wkhrju bighayr 'idhnna, wa'iinaa lajamie mtyqzwn mstedwn lhm"
  26,56,"qal frewn: 'iina bani 'iisrayiyl aladhin frru mae musaa latayft hqyrt qalilat aledd, wa'iinahum lmalywn sdwrna ghyzana; hayth khalfu dynna, wkhrju bighayr 'idhnna, wa'iinaa lajamie mtyqzwn mstedwn lhm"
  26,57,"fakhrj allah fireawn waqawmuh min 'ard \"msr\" dhat albsatyn waeuyun alma' wkhzayn almal walmanazil alhsan. wakama akhrjnahm, jaealna hadhih aldiyar min baedihim libani 'israyyl"
  26,58,"fakhrj allah fireawn waqawmuh min 'ard \"msr\" dhat albsatyn waeuyun alma' wkhzayn almal walmanazil alhsan. wakama akhrjnahm, jaealna hadhih aldiyar min baedihim libani 'israyyl"
  26,59,"fakhrj allah fireawn waqawmuh min 'ard \"msr\" dhat albsatyn waeuyun alma' wkhzayn almal walmanazil alhsan. wakama akhrjnahm, jaealna hadhih aldiyar min baedihim libani 'israyyl"
  26,60,flhq fireawn wjndh musaa wman maeah waqt shrwq alshms
  26,61,"flma ra'aa kl wahid min alfariqayn alakhar qal 'ashab mwsa: 'inn jame fireawn mudrikna wmhlkna"
  26,62,"qal musaa lhm: kla lays al'amr kama dhakartum falan tudraku؛ 'iina maei rabiy balnsr, syhdyny lamaa fih njaty wnjatkm"
  26,63,"fa'awhayna 'iilaa musaa 'an adrib bieasak albhr, fdrb, fanfalaq albahr 'iilaa athny eshr tryqana bieadad qabayil bani 'israyyl, fakanat kl qiteat anfslt min albahr kaljbl alezym"
  26,64,"wqrrabna hunak fireawn waqawmuh hataa dakhaluu albhr, wa'anjayna musaa wman maeah ajmeyn. fastmr albahr ealaa anflaqh hataa eabaruu 'iilaa albr, thuma 'aghraqna fireawn waman maeah b'itbaq albahr ealayhim baed 'an dakhaluu fih mtbeyn musaa wqwmh"
  26,65,"wqrrabna hunak fireawn waqawmuh hataa dakhaluu albhr, wa'anjayna musaa wman maeah ajmeyn. fastmr albahr ealaa anflaqh hataa eabaruu 'iilaa albr, thuma 'aghraqna fireawn waman maeah b'itbaq albahr ealayhim baed 'an dakhaluu fih mtbeyn musaa wqwmh"
  26,66,"wqrrabna hunak fireawn waqawmuh hataa dakhaluu albhr, wa'anjayna musaa wman maeah ajmeyn. fastmr albahr ealaa anflaqh hataa eabaruu 'iilaa albr, thuma 'aghraqna fireawn waman maeah b'itbaq albahr ealayhim baed 'an dakhaluu fih mtbeyn musaa wqwmh"
  26,67,"'in fi dhalik aldhy hadath laebrt ejybt dalt ealaa qudrat allh, wama sar 'akthar 'atbae fireawn muminin mae hadhih aleallamat albahrt"
  26,68,"w'in rabak lahu aleaziz alrhym, bezth 'ahlak alkafirin almkdhbyn, wabirahmatih njja musaa wman maeah ajmeyn"
  26,69,"waqss ealaa alkafirin - 'ayuha alrasul - khabar 'iibrahim hin qal li'abih wqwmh: 'ayu shay' tebdwnh?"
  26,70,"waqss ealaa alkafirin - 'ayuha alrasul - khabar 'iibrahim hin qal li'abih wqwmh: 'ayu shay' tebdwnh?"
  26,71,"qalu: naebud asnamana, fnaekuf ealaa ebadtha"
  26,72,"qal 'iibrahim mnbhana ealaa fasad mdhhbhm: hal yasmaeun duea'akum 'iidh tdewnhm, 'aw yqddimwn lakum nfeana 'iidha ebdtmwhm, 'aw ysybwnkm bidurin 'iidha taraktum ebadthm?"
  26,73,"qal 'iibrahim mnbhana ealaa fasad mdhhbhm: hal yasmaeun duea'akum 'iidh tdewnhm, 'aw yqddimwn lakum nfeana 'iidha ebdtmwhm, 'aw ysybwnkm bidurin 'iidha taraktum ebadthm?"
  26,74,"qaluu: la yakun minhum shay' min dhulika, walakunana wajadna aba'ana yaebudunahum, fqlladnahm fima kanuu yafealuna"
  26,75,"qal 'iibrahima: 'afa'absartum bitadabur maa kuntum taebudun min al'asnam alty la tusmie wala tanfae wala taduru, 'antum wabawukum al'aqdamun min qablikama? fa'iina ma taebudunahum min dun allah 'aeda'an liya, lkna rabu alealamin wamalik 'amrihim hu wahdah aldhy 'aebudah. hu aladhi khalaqani fi 'ahsan suratan fahu yarshaduni 'iilaa masalih aldunya walakhirati, wahu aladhi yaneim ely bialtaeam walsharabi, wa'iidha 'asabani marad fahu aldhy yashfyny wayueafini munhu, wahu aladhi yumituni fi aldiyna biqabd ruhi, thuma yahyini yawm alqiamati, la yuqadar ealaa dhlk ahd sawahan, waladhi 'atmae 'an yatajawaz ean dhinbi yawm aljazaa'a"
  26,76,"qal 'iibrahima: 'afa'absartum bitadabur maa kuntum taebudun min al'asnam alty la tusmie wala tanfae wala taduru, 'antum wabawukum al'aqdamun min qablikama? fa'iina ma taebudunahum min dun allah 'aeda'an liya, lkna rabu alealamin wamalik 'amrihim hu wahdah aldhy 'aebudah. hu aladhi khalaqani fi 'ahsan suratan fahu yarshaduni 'iilaa masalih aldunya walakhirati, wahu aladhi yaneim ely bialtaeam walsharabi, wa'iidha 'asabani marad fahu aldhy yashfyny wayueafini munhu, wahu aladhi yumituni fi aldiyina biqabd ruhi, thuma yahyini yawm alqiamati, la yuqadar ealaa dhlk ahd sawahun, waladhi 'atmae 'an yatajawaz ean dhinbi yawm aljazaa'"
  26,77,"qal 'ibrahym: afabsrtm btdbr maa kuntum taebudun min al'asnam alty la tusmie wala tanfae wala tdr, 'antum wabawukum al'aqdamun min qblkm? fa'iina ma tebdwnhm min dun allah 'aeda'an ly, lkn rabu alealamin wmalk 'amrihim hu wahdah aldhy aebdh. hu aladhi khalaqani fi 'ahsan surat fahu yrshdny 'iilaa masalih aldunya walakhrt, wahu aladhi ynem ely balteam walshrab, wa'iidha asabny marad fahu aldhy yashfyny wyeafyny mnh, wahu aladhi yumituni fi aldyna bqbd rwhy, thuma yhyyny yawm alqyamt, la yuqadar ealaa dhlk ahd swah, waladhi 'atmae 'an yatajawaz ean dhnby yawm aljza'"
  26,78,"qal 'ibrahym: afabsrtm btdbr maa kuntum taebudun min al'asnam alty la tusmie wala tanfae wala tdr, 'antum wabawukum al'aqdamun min qblkm? fa'iina ma tebdwnhm min dun allah 'aeda'an ly, lkn rabu alealamin wmalk 'amrihim hu wahdah aldhy aebdh. hu aladhi khalaqani fi 'ahsan surat fahu yrshdny 'iilaa masalih aldunya walakhrt, wahu aladhi ynem ely balteam walshrab, wa'iidha asabny marad fahu aldhy yashfyny wyeafyny mnh, wahu aladhi yumituni fi aldyna bqbd rwhy, thuma yhyyny yawm alqyamt, la yuqadar ealaa dhlk ahd swah, waladhi 'atmae 'an yatajawaz ean dhnby yawm aljza'"
  26,79,"qal 'ibrahym: afabsrtm btdbr maa kuntum taebudun min al'asnam alty la tusmie wala tanfae wala tdr, 'antum wabawukum al'aqdamun min qblkm? fa'iina ma tebdwnhm min dun allah 'aeda'an ly, lkn rabu alealamin wmalk 'amrihim hu wahdah aldhy aebdh. hu aladhi khalaqani fi 'ahsan surat fahu yrshdny 'iilaa masalih aldunya walakhrt, wahu aladhi ynem ely balteam walshrab, wa'iidha asabny marad fahu aldhy yashfyny wyeafyny mnh, wahu aladhi yumituni fi aldyna bqbd rwhy, thuma yhyyny yawm alqyamt, la yuqadar ealaa dhlk ahd swah, waladhi 'atmae 'an yatajawaz ean dhnby yawm aljza'"
  26,80,"qal 'ibrahym: afabsrtm btdbr maa kuntum taebudun min al'asnam alty la tusmie wala tanfae wala tdr, 'antum wabawukum al'aqdamun min qblkm? fa'iina ma tebdwnhm min dun allah 'aeda'an ly, lkn rabu alealamin wmalk 'amrihim hu wahdah aldhy aebdh. hu aladhi khalaqani fi 'ahsan surat fahu yrshdny 'iilaa masalih aldunya walakhrt, wahu aladhi ynem ely balteam walshrab, wa'iidha asabny marad fahu aldhy yashfyny wyeafyny mnh, wahu aladhi yumituni fi aldyna bqbd rwhy, thuma yhyyny yawm alqyamt, la yuqadar ealaa dhlk ahd swah, waladhi 'atmae 'an yatajawaz ean dhnby yawm aljza'"
